        "description": "Typical beam diameter for industrial cleaning; 100-200 μm for fine surface prep on composites, 300-500 μm for large areas. 200 μm recommended for polyester to ensure uniform energy distribution and avoid localized overheating. Source: Coherent Inc. equipment specifications and industry standards from Laser Institute of America."
